^Land.~, ^Vell.~, ^Dan.~, ^Vent.~, ^Lomb.~, ^Biag.~, ^Costa~,
^Br. B.~, ^Andr.~, ^Triss.~, ^Bennass.~, ^Cam.~, ^Franc.~, ecc.). 
